<li>The Jacobian matrix</li>
<li>The chain rule</li>
<li>The Hessian matrix</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orga08832b" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orga08832b">Partial derivatives and directional derivatives</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orga08832b">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Partial derivatives</li>
<li>Critical points</li>
<li>Inverse function Theorem</li>
<li>Extreme values of a function.</li>
</ul>
</div>
